clearcontrol.devices.cameras

Interface StackCameraDeviceInterface<Q extends StackCameraQueue<Q>>

  • Type Parameters:
    Q - queue type
    All Superinterfaces:
    CameraDeviceInterface, NameableInterface, OpenCloseDeviceInterface, QueueDeviceInterface<Q>, ReadOnlyNameableInterface, ReOpenDeviceInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HamStackCamera, StackCameraDeviceBase, StackCameraDeviceSimulator

    public interface StackCameraDeviceInterface<Q extends StackCameraQueue<Q>>
extends CameraDeviceInterface, QueueDeviceInterface<Q>, NameableInterface
    Interface implemented by all stack cameras. Stack cameras are cameras that in addition to be able to acquire single images can acquire a sequence of images as a stack.
    Author:
    royer
